{"tid":1222512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢， 如果將一條濕毛巾放喺 催淚彈上面夠唔夠水份整熄成個催淚彈？","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:32:19.000Z","uid":147803,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3db37f6fc30a7011c77dce2fd2c1c37262554cd7","tid":1222512,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"我諗緊整一個類似捕蟲網嘅道具。<br />\n用大型濕毛巾取替網袋<br />\n一有催淚彈落地下就成個 捕蟲網cup落去.  一來毛巾可以循環再用, 二來心理上距離長咗都容易應付催淚彈"},{"pid":"49571aedb638238a307888196a8f6dc0528b78fc","tid":1222512,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"毛巾既濕度只能降溫唔夠整熄<br />\n笠完再倒水比較好"},{"pid":"ac5bfa5ef7e48ae2a51bdf4c950868403723d080","tid":1222512,"uid":147803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49571aedb638238a307888196a8f6dc0528b78fc","tid":1222512,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"毛巾既濕度只能降溫唔夠整熄<br />\n笠完再倒水比較好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"雙管齊下， 笠實之後其他人倒水冇咁大心理壓力"},{"pid":"5502af1967c84bf67bd976ae05e903aaca57842b","tid":1222512,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"如果設計來講 最好簡單組裝 廢物利用 有一定距離 方便倒水"},{"pid":"7536b3a2dbbcf5b2c28970ac8ac81b38edfc0de7","tid":1222512,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"空芯水管 + 濕毛巾<br />\n毛巾裝係上面，打直咁拎<br />\n水管裝水<br />\n當你拍落粒蛋果度，水順住流出黎<br />\n行近都唔駛"},{"pid":"46ae691c1cce8cbcc34c87c54092731fa2a34a8a","tid":1222512,"uid":256899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"我地整翻水炮車"},{"pid":"bfda70e0d203b24453856ee3dab450ea0c55f431","tid":1222512,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7536b3a2dbbcf5b2c28970ac8ac81b38edfc0de7","tid":1222512,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"空芯水管 + 濕毛巾<br />\n毛巾裝